You were just plain unlucky. Both scrolls were cursed, so they level
teleported you (to a random level instead of within the level you were
on) and in both cases you happened to end up on the level you were
already on. If you get teleported to a different level the scroll has to
find a place for you to land, but you already had a place on your
destination level (the place where you were standing), so...

Raisse, killed by burning scrolls

